<br>
3rd floor is easier than 2nd floor.  5th floor is easier than 4th floor.  Etc.<br>
<br>
On the first floor, those drovalg things on the first floor are under-cons, I'd stick to soloing the skeletons (all the rooms to the left of the entrance have skels in the, as does the pit in the center).<br>
<br>
2nd floor is all casters.  Really hard to solo, but once you get the spawn broken up with a group it's really easy.  They have crap for HP and if ya don't let them buff up you can knock 'em over like dominos.<br>
<br>
- Syll<br>
