<br>
On the 2nd floor, monsters path towards the entrance mirror until they're lined up with a bookcase row, then towards the center of the room, and then back towards the 3rd floor mirror (careful when they get there, because they'll occasionally pull 3rd floor mobs if just left there screaming for aggro).<br>
<br>
- Syll <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/usiffo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Siffo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silly old Rogue</span><br>  Posts: 164<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(9/26/02 8:03:40 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2792.topic&index=27>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Rogue Hunting Grounds</span><hr size=1> Of zoning into a mob or groups of mobs.<br>
